#🚗 RideEase – Modern Ride-Hailing Platform

Welcome to **RideEase**, a sleek and secure ride-hailing web application redefining urban transportation. 
Designed for ease, safety, and affordability, RideEase offers real-time ride booking with multiple vehicle options and an innovative **Buddy Ride** system.

---

## 🌟 Key Features

### 🚘 Multiple Ride Options
- **RideEase Mini** – Compact 4-seater for daily commutes 🧳  
- **RideEase Sedan** – Premium comfort, perfect for business travel 💼  
- **RideEase Moto** – Fast single-seater bike for quick city trips 🏍️  
- **AutoEase** – 3-seater auto rickshaw for short rides on a budget 🚜  

---

### 🛡️ Safety-Focused
- **Pink Rides** – Female-only rides with verified female drivers 👩‍🦰  
- **Real-Time Tracking** – Monitor your ride from pickup to drop-off 📍  
- **Secure Payments** – Pay safely with Card, Wallet, or Cash 💳  
- **Verified Drivers** – Every driver is background-checked ✅  

---

### 🤝 Buddy Ride System
- Share rides with others heading your way 🚘➡️🚘  
- **Split Fare** – Automatically divide ride cost 💸  
- Create or join rides in real-time  
- Female-only buddy rides for added safety  

---

### 🧑‍💻 User-Centric Design
- Real-time fare estimator  
- Google Maps integration with accurate driver ETA  
- Multi-language support: 🇬🇧 English | 🇮🇳 Hindi | 🇪🇸 Español  
- Detect current location for quick booking  
- Schedule rides for later 🕒  

---

## 🧰 Tech Stack

| Layer | Tools |
|-------|-------|
| **Frontend** | HTML5, Tailwind CSS, JavaScript |
| **Maps** | Google Maps API |
| **Auth** | Firebase Authentication |
| **Realtime** | Firebase Realtime Database |
| **PWA** | Fully installable Progressive Web App |

---

## 🚀 Booking Experience

1. Enter **pickup** and **drop-off** locations  
2. Get **instant fare estimates**  
3. Choose your ride (Mini, Sedan, Moto, AutoEase)  
4. Opt for **Buddy Ride** if desired  
5. Select **payment mode** and **confirm**  
6. Track your ride live until you reach safely 🛡️  

---


## 🛠️ Setup & Run Locally

```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/your-username/rideease.git
cd rideease

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Set up environment
cp .env.example .env
# Add your Firebase and Google Maps API keys

# Run the development server
npm run dev
